        <h1>Global Health repository</h1>
        <p>This document is a draft 'user specification' for a resource repository for the Global Health project, managed by Catrin Evans. Note that due to funding and time constraints, only a pilot repository may be developed in the first instance, which will act both as a usable repository and 'seed' for future funding to develop a fully-featured repository.</p>

